OL,3,CPossible industrial action by
OL,4,Cfirefighters may close island airport
OL,6,FJersey Airport firefighters will vote
OL,7,Fon industrial action in a dispute over
OL,8,Fpensions.
OL,10,FThe trade union Prospect claims that
OL,11,FPorts of Jersey (PoJ) has barred new
OL,12,Fjoiners from the Public Employees'
OL,13,FPension Fund scheme.
OL,15,FFirefighters will now be balloted on
OL,16,Fbeginning industrial action which
OL,17,Fcould see future airport closures.
OL,19,FPoJ says it would manage potential
OL,20,Fdisruption and is pursuing legal
OL,21,Fproceedings against Prospect.
