OL,3,CPossible industrial action by
OL,4,Cfirefighters may close island airport
OL,6,FProspect National Secretary Bob King
OL,7,Fsays airport firefighters are the only
OL,8,Feligible emergency service workers on
OL,9,Fthe island to be denied access to the
OL,10,Fpension scheme.
OL,12,FHe explains: "The changes made will
OL,13,Fforce firefighters to work to at least
OL,14,Fage 67 whilst maintaining a high level
OL,15,Fof fitness and the ability to
OL,16,Fundertake significant physical tasks.
