OL,6,F"The people of Jersey will understand
OL,7,Fthat we have been left with no choice
OL,8,Fbut to take this action as we know
OL,9,Fthey value their emergency services
OL,10,Fand we hope they will support us in
OL,11,Four call for equal treatment."
OL,13,FPorts of Jersey says it introduced a
OL,14,Fdefined contribution occupational
OL,15,Fretirement scheme for all new joiners
OL,16,Fin 2020 and still contribute between
OL,17,F5% and 10% into each employee's
OL,18,Fpension pot.
