OL,6,FPoJ states: "The Airport Fire Service
OL,7,Fsubmitted a formal collective
OL,8,Fgrievance about these pension
OL,9,Farrangements and we have reached stage
OL,10,Fthree of an agreed four-stage dispute
OL,11,Fresolution process.
OL,13,F"Earlier this year Prospect said they
OL,14,Fwere opting out of the process and
OL,15,Fthat they plan to ballot for
OL,16,Findustrial action.
OL,18,F"This has left us with no alternative
OL,19,Fbut to issue legal proceedings against
OL,20,FProspect."
